data.description: Are you looking for closest space??? How about not one but 2 WALK-IN CLOSETS plus a big ass primary bathroom! Try finding that in St. Pete on a double lot!!!! This exquisite split-bedroom floorplan boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 luxurious baths, providing ample space for your family to thrive. Step inside and be captivated by the expansive rooms adorned with gleaming hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance to every corner. The crown molding exudes an air of sophistication, showcasing the meticulous attention to detail. Closet space will never be an issue with the giant closets that offer room for all your wardrobe essentials and then some. All systems and roof only 7 years old! Enjoy the convenience of covered parking with four off-street spots! Situated on an enchanting oak-lined street, this home is a sanctuary of calm, with not one but two spacious lots on a corner, providing an abundance of breathing room and a sense of openness that's truly special. Experience the perfect blend of convenience and charm, as you're just a stone's throw away from five grocery stores, an array of delectable restaurants, and a variety of retail options. Stay fit and healthy with easy access to gyms for your daily workouts. Don't let the proximity to 275 fool you - this home offers peace and serenity, shielded from any unwanted noise. Plus, the paved alley access adds an extra layer of accessibility. Downtown is a mere 10 minutes away, ensuring you're never far from the vibrant energy of the urban landscape. Exciting news for investors or those with an eye for potential - this property falls under the new NTM zoning, allowing for up to four units per parcel. Imagine the endless possibilities for creating your own oasis or investing in a thriving community.
